   Pu, Ziyuan, Minist Transport, Key Lab Transport Ind Comprehens Transportat Theor, Nanjing Modern Multimodal Transportat Lab, Nanjing, Peoples R China.
   Cui, Zhiyong, Beihang Univ, Sch Transportat Sci \& Engn, Beijing, Peoples R China.
   Lee, Seunghyeon, Univ Seoul, Dept Transportat Engn, Seoul, South Korea.
   Ngoduy, Dong, Monash Univ, Dept Civil Engn, Melbourne, Australia.},
