Affiliation = {Wu, XW; Ren, JA (Corresponding Author), Nanjing Univ, Jinling Hosp, Affiliated Hosp, Res Inst Gen Surg,Med Sch, Nanjing, Peoples R China.
   Zhao, Y (Corresponding Author), Nanjing Med Univ, BenQ Med Ctr, Dept Gen Surg, Affiliated BenQ Hosp, Nanjing 210019, Peoples R China.
