   Gong, Wenbin, Southeast Univ, Sch Med, Nanjing 210002, Peoples R China.
   Zheng, Tao; Wu, Jie; Xie, Haohao; Jiang, Haiyang; Zhao, Yun, Nanjing Med Univ, BenQ Med Ctr, Dept Gen Surg, Affiliated BenQ Hosp, Nanjing 210019, Peoples R China.
   Fan, Yong; Liu, Xiaoli; Zhang, Zhengbo, Chinese Peoples Liberat Army Gen Hosp, Ctr Artificial Intelligence Med, Beijing 100039, Peoples R China.},
