   Sturmer, Til, UNC Gillings Sch Global Publ Hlth, Dept Epidemiol, 2101 B McGavran-Greenberg Hall CB 7435, Chapel Hill, NC 27599 USA.
   Kosorok, Michael R., UNC Gillings Sch Global Publ Hlth, Dept Biostat, 3105H McGavran Greenberg Hall CB 7420, Chapel Hill, NC 27599 USA.},
