   Rahbar, Mohammad H., Univ Texas Hlth Sci Ctr Houston, Div Clin \& Translat Sci, Dept Internal Med, Sch Med, Houston, TX 77030 USA.
   Schreiber, Martin A., Oregon Hlth \& Sci Univ, Sch Med, Div Trauma Crit Care \& Acute Care Surg, Portland, OR 97201 USA.
   Alarcon, Louis H., Univ Pittsburgh, Sch Med, Dept Surg, Div Trauma \& Gen Surg, Pittsburgh, PA USA.
   Brasel, Karen J., Med Coll Wisconsin, Dept Surg, Div Trauma \& Crit Care, Milwaukee, WI 53226 USA.
