   Zhang, Yin; Hu, Qingwu, Wuhan Univ, Sch Remote Sensing \& Informat Engn, Wuhan, Peoples R China.
   Ma, Weibo; Lei, Shaogang, China Univ Min \& Technol, Sch Environm \& Spatial Informat, Xuzhou, Peoples R China.
   Hu, Qingwu, Wuhan Univ, Hubei LuoJia Lab, Wuhan, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1080/15481603.2025.2483492},
