   Agard, Geoffray; Boyer, Laurent; Hraiech, Sami, Aix Marseille Univ, Fac Med, Ctr Etud Rech Serv Sante Qual Vie CERESS, EA 3279, F-13005 Marseille, France.
   Agard, Geoffray; Roman, Christophe; Ouladsine, Mustapha, Aix Marseille Univ, Lab Informat \& Syst LIS, UMR 7020, AMU,CNRS,UTLN, Campus St Jerome Bat Polytech, F-13013 Marseille, France.
   Boyer, Laurent; Hraiech, Sami, Hop Conception, AP HM, Dept Informat Med, F-13005 Marseille, France.},
