   Chapman, Cole G., Univ Iowa, Dept Pharm Practice \& Sci Iowa City, Iowa, LA USA.
   Chapman, Cole G.; Chen, Brian K.; Floyd, Sarah B.; Hikmet, Neset, Ctr Effectiveness Res Orthopaed, Greenville, SC USA.
   Floyd, Sarah B., Clemson Univ, Publ Hlth Sci, Coll Behav Social \& Hlth Sci, Clemson, SC USA.
   Hikmet, Neset, Univ South Carolina, USC, Dept Integrated Informat Technol, Coll Engn \& Comp,Innovat Think Tank Lab, Columbia, SC USA.},
DOI = {10.1186/s12874-024-02187-5},
