Affiliation = {Tong, XW (Corresponding Author), Beijing Normal Univ, Sch Stat, Beijing 100875, Peoples R China.
   Wu, Peng; Hu, Qi-rui; Tong, Xing-wei, Beijing Normal Univ, Sch Stat, Beijing 100875, Peoples R China.
