Affiliation = {Zhou, LY; Guo, L (Corresponding Author), Huazhong Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Architecture \& Urban Planning, Wuhan, Peoples R China.
   Yang, Shuo; Zhou, Leyu; Li, Haidong; Guo, Liang, Huazhong Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Architecture \& Urban Planning, Wuhan, Peoples R China.
