   Falcone, Jeremy, Hop Huriez, Ctr Hosp Univ Lille, Lille, France.
   Charbonneau, Helene, Clin Pasteur, Dept Anesthesiol \& Intens Care Unit, Toulouse, France.
   Delaporte, Amelie; Joosten, Alexandre, Univ Calif Los Angeles, David Geffen Sch Med, Dept Anesthesiol \& Perioperat Med, Los Angeles, CA USA.
   Lemoine, Adrien, Sorbonne Univ, Hop Tenon, APHP, Serv Anesthesie Reanimat \& Medecine Perioperatoire, Paris, France.
